original: BRYNJE, Roland Viktor, Grosshandlare, Norrköping, f Norrkp 19/7 97. Inneh Knut Anderson AB, Norrkp, konserver o sydfrukter i parti, grund 92.
translated: BRYNJE, Roland Viktor, Wholesale Merchant, Norrköping, born in Norrköping on July 19th, 1897. Owned Knut Anderson AB, Norrköping, dealing in canned goods and tropical fruits in bulk, established in 1892. Note: '\d\d m. partners name' indicates that the person got married in the year 19xx.
